Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\bord0\shad0\fs127.5}愛的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,金 我們一起去慶典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說我們倆一起去 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我說金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這等煙花盛景 你不好好觀看多可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡真是一處特等席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我還要給店裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 團長還在等我 先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,咱待會兒也過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,咱這個笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這是人類與非人類還同處於一個世界的古老故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克森 德雷弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,奪回被兩大聖騎士長所支配的王都之戰已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是聖戰的預兆猶在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如今又將燃起新的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他們說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他們就在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,七原罪就在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,師父你也喝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,班 剩飯要變成啤酒味啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你要變成芳香醇厚的豬肉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白回去後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看板娘就是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然後咱和戴安一起去採購
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜店裡的大叔說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可愛的新婚夫婦可享優惠價
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然後咱問戴安是否覺得困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,結果她說 不 我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,難不成戴安對咱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真蠢 真蠢 真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安喜歡的是團長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但之前她又邀請了咱參加慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你去問一下本人不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,豬君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有時候不挑明會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你太沒出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你也說說他啊 你個混蛋狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,住口 你個混蛋狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要讓你明白誰更厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,會吃壞肚子的哦 奧斯羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不來一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喝我的酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是一點都不懂得節制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 豪澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我得吃藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,藥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是讓我身體變小的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是變大的話會嚇到大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 小剩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我會吃得有滋有味的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小剩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 金大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有需要的話 我給你倒杯水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白大人 你難道是在收拾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 團長居然讓公主大人做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只會做這些而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只能幫上梅利奧達斯大人的一點點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,團長 你聽到剛才的話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,咱勸你偶爾也要向伊麗莎白大人表達一下感激之情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我無時無刻不在感激伊麗莎白哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,團長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 倒是你向人家道謝了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝得酩酊大醉 戴安片刻不離陪在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,整整一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咱好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,頭好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安一早就出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她說中午回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,咱…咱去找一下戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,別去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能想一個人待著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在之前的戰鬥之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,鎮上的人們似乎曾對她施以兵戎 惡語相加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說他們是被德雷弗斯聖騎士長煽動的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但對她來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,或許待在人類的國度本身就是種煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話我都不知道該怎麼安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,豪澤爾 你完全沒必要安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的交給咱就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經受夠人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,別來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,永別了 金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,難道她就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能幫我把那個搬到這裡來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,咱滑啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 多虧了小姑娘你每天過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,修復工作進行得很順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的力氣好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我給這一帶的人添過麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,七原罪 嫉妒之罪戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那個時候的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我靠瑪琳的藥變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一定很怕我 很討厭我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我嚇到了大家 毀壞了小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想為這一切道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你們不原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想盡可能幫上大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要向我們道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才是做了即使道歉也難求原諒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候我們的行為很過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一心以為七原罪是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真心感到慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再不趕緊工作的話 太陽就要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒 各位 重新開工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前先吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你若不介意 就一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你都看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎麼不來一起幫忙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不 咱感覺咱不適合出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話 咱沒有原諒那些人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安還是一如既往很善良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你想 咱說的一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那個不是說兩百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而是15年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,兩百年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,咱有這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咱和戴安的初遇是在15年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那兩百年前是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…那是…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,咱給你買了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦 我看看就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,金做的衣服更可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我說金 你餓不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不 咱就是突然想跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我說金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,回店裡之前 我們來玩追人遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,追人遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我老早想在這鎮上玩一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在的大小能玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 這次換我來逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,金要是能抓住我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以答應你任何一個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是能抓住咱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,咱可以答應你任何一個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你好狡猾啊 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,才不狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看咱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你能飛那麼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還遠遠不止這點程度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你就這麼想讓我答應你一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 你加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何 咱都要抓到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,咱想讓戴安做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,陪咱約會一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,別黏那麼緊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,陪咱睡一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或者和咱一起戲水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好色呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 然後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 咱跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去咱的野心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼在此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,二位能夠發誓永遠愛對方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我以女神之名 認可二位結為夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好好加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你頭上沾了片花瓣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,金 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,人類因為壽命短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他們會通過結婚的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,結成連理將生命維繫下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對於壽命很畏的我們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是沒有意義的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很令人羨慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那句話 是咱從前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,救…救命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,新世代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安 你待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這次我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,金 要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要想只打敗魔神的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就唯有攻擊那個聖騎士體內的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一招了結牠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等咱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,咱現在就來救你 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,休想妨礙金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,合技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,十字射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我被你抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼兌現承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以答應金任何一個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 什麼都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,咱希望你回答咱一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你恢復當年的記憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣回答你可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 所以你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安 關於今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…咱…咱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,和你之間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咱感覺發生了一件非常好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,咱記得咱出門去找戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…然後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說你忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道啊 是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,咱好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,咱這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52}時間啊 倒流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,終
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的梅利奧達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的傷太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還不是睡覺的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎 德雷弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克森
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我一看到你的臉就突然這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我犯了很多無法挽回的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:22:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也做過對不起你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讓我睡去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我的身體已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,德雷弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吾友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我等的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 七原罪 聖戰的預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,剩飯長說了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,團長做菜那就是剩飯的預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是遺憾的預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,遺憾的剩飯？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}霞光萬道中你吹著口哨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}「明天見」「再會」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.76,OP,,0,0,0,,那理所當然的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.97,OP,,0,0,0,,竟被3、2、1、0重置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}神明大人也會一笑置之吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:10.69,OP,,0,0,0,,仰望天空 擺出一副幸福姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:15.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}摘下枯萎的最後一株幸運草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:20.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}如果世界讓你哭泣 我願為你犯下任何罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}光明降臨 Regret
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.71,OP,,0,0,0,,破壞吧 Never Ever Heaven's Blind World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.33,OP,,0,0,0,,泡沫之夢消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:34.17,OP,,0,0,0,,曾幾何時目及的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:38.63,OP,,0,0,0,,如果你能面露微笑 我願為你承受任何懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:43.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}拂曉的Blurry Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:49.19,OP,,0,0,0,,明天若吹起口哨 小小的瞳孔深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:54.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}必將閃現光輝未來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:06.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}著眼於未來的背影中看不到一絲迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:14.94,ED,,0,0,0,,我的心中燃起了星星之火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:23.70,ED,,0,0,0,,我憧憬著你 跟著你的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:31.46,ED,,0,0,0,,回過神來已是氣喘吁吁 我這才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:40.59,ED,,0,0,0,,我未知的潛能 還被壓在箱底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:49.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}黑暗之中黑天墨地 我用心中生鏽的鑰匙撬開箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:59.98,ED,,0,0,0,,你有只屬於你的特別色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:08.37,ED,,0,0,0,,不論誰試圖塗抹你 你的色彩都光芒四射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:16.75,ED,,0,0,0,,各自的色彩交匯浸染 頑強地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:24.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}你的一切 由我守護
